snippet.title: Pro Arts
snippet.description:
I am a Professional Landscape Artist based in Scotland. I have sold over 500 paintings to date all over the world in USA, Canada, Dubai, Germany, NewYork, Orlando, UK, Norway to just name a few. I also have an Art Licensing contract which sell prints of my work in the USA and Canada, Walmart, Art.com, the big canvas company and so many more. 

I am pleased to share and pass on my tips and ideas about making Art special, different and to stand out from the rest. Quirky tips and ideas from a colourist in Contemporary Impressionistic Art.

I will be making a drawing a day. How to draw a.... (whatever you wish me to draw)  I hope this journey brings you fun, joy and entertainment in Art World

Please ask away if you want me to draw anything at all, I’m always up for a challenge and I will break down exactly how I make ART sellable. 

Hit that subscribe button if you want to see more valuable tips and tutorials of everything Art with Oils, acrylics and Posca Pens. 

Caroline Duncan ART
